These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, cola
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | juice  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | mystery   |
| Sport         | sailing | water-polo |
| Transport     | airplane | van    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, lemon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, horror
2 different pets are kept: fish, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, quad-bike
1. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | zucchini     | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | adventure  |
| Pet           | cat         | fish     |
| Transport     | van   | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
