The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, mechanic
2 different pets are kept: fish, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | lemonade     | tea |
| Job         | mechanic | lawyer    |
| Pet         | fish         | pony        |
| Transport   | quad-bike         | motorbike    |

