There 2 different types of food: avocado, peach
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | water     | milk |
| Food          | peach   | avocado  |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | photography     |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | reggae         |

