.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, fisherman
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
2. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fisherman is the colombian##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | fisherman | software-developer    |
| Nationality   | colombian       | japanese |
| Pet           | rabbit         | hedgehog    |
| Sport         | basketball    | parkour   |

